{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Probably I'm much older now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But anyhow, she was an invalid lady, and she had a special diet-- liver problems, and needed bananas.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Ruth got friendly with the nuns, and was able to get these nuns to take the-- they weren't used to criminals like poor old Frau Han, you know, who had never had hurt a fly in her life, you know.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all these girls were brought in from the school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The girls that were old enough to be in their teens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these nuns couldn't figure out-- are these prostitutes, are they thieves, what are they?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't know enough about Hitler and Mussolini.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these were hostages-- in case anything should happen to our Fuhrer-- why, their life was not going to be very good.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were hostages for-- for Hitler to get back safe to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, we never prayed so hard that Hitler would get back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as soon as he got back to Germany-- took-- I don't know how long they were in jail-- a few weeks, short time-- Hitler went back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they all decided, we've got to get out of here soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kempner immediately wrote to America, where friends of his mother in Philadelphia wrote back to him-- a shame your mother didn't stay in America anyway.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But since she was-- a shame you studied law-- we could help you if you were medical people-- but come anyway.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We will see to it that you are helped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if you don't have enough money, we will see to it that you're taken care of.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went very shortly after that, with difficulty through France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And arrived the day, in New York, the day the war began.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
